# Project Summary: Bank Customer Segmentation Analysis

## 🎯 Problem
Understand customer behavior and segment users to improve marketing and revenue strategies.

## 🛠 Approach
- Cleaned and transformed data in Power BI  
- Performed customer segmentation analysis  
- Built interactive dashboard for insights  

## 📊 Insights
- Revenue is driven by a small customer segment  
- Customers are concentrated in specific regions  
- Several high-balance customers show low engagement  
